i'm looking for cloud storage for my personal files. right now i'm using MEGA, 50gb with free account. But i have this paranoid that they'll shut down their services anytime in near future, even though the founder says [it's not safe anymore because government takeover](https://www.businessinsider.com/kim-dotcom-data-not-safe-filing-sharing-site-mega-2015-7?IR=T).

Since my files are mostly photos (raw) and videos, i looked at Google Photos. It's more organized than MEGA, better image & video viewing and stuffs. So, is it worthy Rp269.000 a year for 100GB? or should i wait till my MEGA account exceed 50GB then migrate to Google for menghemat duit?
